|---|---|---|---|
| ![fox\_5](https://redirect.github.com/user-attachments/assets/8876ebb0-fea2-4443-b458-fdd6c035a69f) | ![fox\_6](https://redirect.github.com/user-attachments/assets/1989f128-5fd4-4b0c-83b4-dc5f33b388c2) | ![fox\_7](https://redirect.github.com/user-attachments/assets/1fa9ac58-ca14-4ee3-84ca-47e69de2589c) | ![fox\_8](https://redirect.github.com/user-attachments/assets/20a20642-a336-4277-9056-f45d7ddb3bbe) |

